            "id": 6124950,
            "title": "《異動股》易方達恒指ESG升近3%破頂,現報3.92元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社25日專訊》易方達恒指ESG(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03039:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03039\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03039-HK</a>)一度升近3%,最高價見3.922元,創上市新高,現升2.9%,報3.92元,最低價3.918元;成交24.1萬股,成交金額94.44萬元;主動買沽比率100:0,資金淨主動買入94.44萬元。現時最大淨被動賣出券商為FLOW　TRADERS　HK,金額69.38萬元,加權平均成交價3.919元。以現價計,該股暫連升2日,累計升幅3.8%。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　基本資料</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　====</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>現價</td><td>3.920</td><td>變動</td><td>+2.89%</td></tr><tr><td>最高價</td><td>3.922</td><td>最低價</td><td>3.918</td></tr><tr><td>成交股數</td><td>24.1萬股</td><td>成交金額</td><td>94.44萬</td></tr><tr><td>10天平均</td><td>3.789</td><td>歷史波幅%</td><td>16.833</td></tr><tr><td>20天平均</td><td>3.746</td><td>加權平均價</td><td>3.919</td></tr><tr><td>50天平均</td><td>3.641</td><td>RSI14</td><td>71.962</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">股份狀態:創上市新高;主動買沽比率100:0,資金淨主動買入94.44萬元;暫連升2日,累計升幅3.8%</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　表列同板塊或相關股份表現</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　============</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>股份(編號)</td><td>現價(元)</td><td>變幅(%)</td></tr><tr><td>易方達恒指ESG(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03039:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03039\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03039-HK</a>)</td><td>3.920</td><td>+2.89</td></tr><tr><td>標智香港100(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02825:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02825\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02825-HK</a>)</td><td>29.700</td><td>+2.34</td></tr><tr><td>東匯香港35(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03012:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03012\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03012-HK</a>)</td><td>18.880</td><td>+1.51</td></tr><tr><td>平安香港高息(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03070:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03070\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03070-HK</a>)</td><td>37.680</td><td>+0.86</td></tr><tr><td>GX恒生高股息率(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03110:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03110\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03110-HK</a>)</td><td>30.660</td><td>+0.52</td></tr><tr><td>南方港股通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03432:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03432\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03432-HK</a>)</td><td>119.000</td><td>+1.58</td></tr><tr><td>華夏恒生生科-U(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09069:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09069\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09069-HK</a>)</td><td>2.248美元</td><td>+0.45</td></tr><tr><td>安碩恒生指數-U