/quote/01478\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01478-HK</a>)</td><td>15.09</td><td>-0.20</td></tr><tr><td>小米(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01810:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01810\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01810-HK</a>)</td><td>53.45</td><td>+1.71</td></tr><tr><td>瑞聲科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02018:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02018\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02018-HK</a>)</td><td>44.76</td><td>-1.32</td></tr><tr><td>舜宇光學科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02382-HK</a>)</td><td>83.95</td><td>+3.45</td></tr><tr><td>阿里(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09988:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09988\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09988-HK</a>)</td><td>124.90</td><td>+5.85</td></tr><tr><td>聯想集團-R(80992-HK)</td><td>10.31人幣</td><td>+4.46</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　(ed)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
